  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ef33e7f54975e1c1d585d5be34e93a8a.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abnormality</strong> is a realistic co-op ghost-hunting horror game where you investigate abandoned, restricted locations, gather evidence, identify the ghost, and survive the hunt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0afa2a6ed6efd821093ed31e902be5d0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigations begin in <strong>daytime</strong>, giving you time to explore, learn the map, and prepare before the danger truly begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As <strong>night falls</strong>, the atmosphere shifts, visibility drops, and the ghosts begin to emerge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike slower ghost-hunting games, <strong>Abnormality</strong> lets you actually <strong>sprint</strong>, allowing for real chases where movement, awareness, and quick decisions matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When darkness takes over, <strong>night vision</strong> becomes your last resort.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/b4b344fedd667562c19a45e5e7e646f0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INVESTIGATION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A classic ghost-hunting experience featuring <strong>20 different ghost types</strong>, each with their own behaviours, personality, known traits, and hidden traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghosts vary in <strong>speed, hunt duration, aggression, and more</strong>, meaning no two investigations feel exactly the same. Figure out the ghost type, survive the hunt, and make it out alive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXORCISM MODE (COMING SOON)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A sequel to Investigation, where you enter <strong>after previous investigators have already identified the haunting</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the same locations, but far more terrifying, this intense gamemode is not for the weak. Exorcise the ghost by uncovering its trauma, learning why it will not let go, and pray you do not get a demon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THIEF MODE & SURVIVAL MODE (TBA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More gamemodes are planned, including <strong>Thief Mode</strong> and <strong>Survival Mode</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/3f044758b344608b228f267da58881f0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a character that feels personal with detailed customization options including appearance, body features, skin tone, clothing, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lobby customization</strong> is also planned to arrive in a future update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/caa9f19d36361f514cf86fb9d446968e.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror is the heart of <strong>Abnormality</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every location is fully <strong>abandoned</strong>, meaning <strong>no electricity, no working lights</strong>, and a much more unsettling atmosphere. Ghosts are highly <strong>active, intense, and unpredictable</strong>, with different traits that make each encounter feel terrifying in its own way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect <strong>jumpscares, screen shake, being dragged away from your friends</strong>, and even <strong>possession mechanics</strong> planned for the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is dark, set in creepy environments, and <strong>audio has been a major focus</strong> to make every moment feel more immersive and disturbing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/c26813308583e037be80e9d9f35a8d92.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate a variety of haunted locations, including <strong>houses, a manor, a chapel, a motel</strong>, and maps that change the flow of gameplay, such as a location consumed by a <strong>blizzard</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each location also contains hidden story elements that reveal why the ghost exists and what happened before you arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/978fdb769f2b301703ca03c74adebe7d.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the ghost-hunting tools players know and love, alongside new additions designed to make every investigation more immersive and intense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate by day. Survive the night.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ef33e7f54975e1c1d585d5be34e93a8a.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abnormality</strong> is a realistic co-op ghost-hunting horror game where you investigate abandoned, restricted locations, gather evidence, identify the ghost, and survive the hunt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0afa2a6ed6efd821093ed31e902be5d0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/f0223c000feb71c81930fdf570e0971d.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigations begin in <strong>daytime</strong>, giving you time to explore, learn the map, and prepare before the danger truly begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As <strong>night falls</strong>, the atmosphere shifts, visibility drops, and the ghosts begin to emerge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike slower ghost-hunting games, <strong>Abnormality</strong> lets you actually <strong>sprint</strong>, allowing for real chases where movement, awareness, and quick decisions matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When darkness takes over, <strong>night vision</strong> becomes your last resort.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/b4b344fedd667562c19a45e5e7e646f0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/ce3a27e1e679a71e519f347e7d08bb7e.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INVESTIGATION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A classic ghost-hunting experience featuring <strong>20 different ghost types</strong>, each with their own behaviours, personality, known traits, and hidden traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghosts vary in <strong>speed, hunt duration, aggression, and more</strong>, meaning no two investigations feel exactly the same. Figure out the ghost type, survive the hunt, and make it out alive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXORCISM MODE (COMING SOON)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A sequel to Investigation, where you enter <strong>after previous investigators have already identified the haunting</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the same locations, but far more terrifying, this intense gamemode is not for the weak. Exorcise the ghost by uncovering its trauma, learning why it will not let go, and pray you do not get a demon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THIEF MODE & SURVIVAL MODE (TBA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More gamemodes are planned, including <strong>Thief Mode</strong> and <strong>Survival Mode</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/3f044758b344608b228f267da58881f0.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1ccbbc19d48e0262cddd8f30e1f4e8c5.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a character that feels personal with detailed customization options including appearance, body features, skin tone, clothing, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lobby customization</strong> is also planned to arrive in a future update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/caa9f19d36361f514cf86fb9d446968e.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/e9fa0934fa5e2ec355df7718b104cdec.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror is the heart of <strong>Abnormality</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every location is fully <strong>abandoned</strong>, meaning <strong>no electricity, no working lights</strong>, and a much more unsettling atmosphere. Ghosts are highly <strong>active, intense, and unpredictable</strong>, with different traits that make each encounter feel terrifying in its own way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect <strong>jumpscares, screen shake, being dragged away from your friends</strong>, and even <strong>possession mechanics</strong> planned for the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is dark, set in creepy environments, and <strong>audio has been a major focus</strong> to make every moment feel more immersive and disturbing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/c26813308583e037be80e9d9f35a8d92.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/0ad866ace3054a7522f380161359b4f3.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate a variety of haunted locations, including <strong>houses, a manor, a chapel, a motel</strong>, and maps that change the flow of gameplay, such as a location consumed by a <strong>blizzard</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each location also contains hidden story elements that reveal why the ghost exists and what happened before you arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/978fdb769f2b301703ca03c74adebe7d.webp?t=1774299769\" width=543 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.poster.avif?t=1774299769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.webm?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541890/extras/1a70071672bfe172932f708a48372996.mp4?t=1774299769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the ghost-hunting tools players know and love, alongside new additions designed to make every investigation more immersive and intense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate by day. Survive the night.</strong></p>",
